After so many requests I'm reuploading my Taylor Swift Upscales. All videos upscaled from the highest quality Master or ProRes file I could find. (Only Look What You Made Me Do is a rip from 4K ProRes) If a video is not here it means I don't have it in a good quality that would worth my time to upscale. If I obtain new videos I'm planning to update the folder. You can also send me the ProRes files and I would upscale them.

I won't upload my 1080p upscales since other people already upscaled them with ProRes resources and they look better. If I also get them (Picture to Burn, Change, You Belong With Me etc.) in ProRes I'd also upload them. Also can't promise another reupload if the folder is removed.
